snippet.title: MetaOps: Gameplay Trailer | NFT-Based First-Person Shooter Built On The Solana Blockchain
snippet.description:
You will love this game if you like Halo and Call of Duty. Join the battlefield, team up with friends, advance your characters, level up your weapons, and earn in-game tokens and NFTs with every in-game kill.

You can buy, sell and trade all digital assets earned in the game, such as items, weapons, characters, skins, collectibles, and skills.

MetaOps allows players to experience the metaverse from the eyes of a first-person shooter. Take part in the lore of their campaign mode, or battle it out in the multiplayer mode.

Learn more about MetaOps ► http://metaopsgaming.com/
Buy MetaOps NFTs ► https://www.fractal.is/metaops

FOLLOW METAOPS ON: 
📂 Discord: https://discord.com/metaops
🕊Twitter: https://twitter.com/MetaOpsGaming
📸 Instagram: https://instagram.com/metaopsgaming
🧑‍💼 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MetaOpsGaming
🎥 Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/metaopsgaming

MetaOps was created by a #blockchain company, Open Portal Studios, with the mission to place more power in the hands of the players by providing connection to the #metaverse via in-game NFTs. 

#MetaOps #Solana #NFTs #SolanaNFTs
